translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_a5818b0d:

    # mc "I mean, it's a great location for someone at the University, but I can't imagine a college student..."
    mc "Maksud saya, ini adalah lokasi yang bagus untuk seseorang di Universiti, tetapi saya tidak dapat membayangkan seorang pelajar kolej..."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:85
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_6779bbcd:

    # mh "Yeah. So, not for you."
    mh "Yeah. Jadi, bukan untuk awak."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:86
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_ad122613:

    # mc "I mean, I'm looking for someplace across town, closer to the College..."
    mc "Maksud saya, saya mencari tempat di seberang bandar, lebih dekat dengan Kolej..."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:89
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_d09f83d7:

    # mh "Oh?"
    mh "Oh?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:90
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_e5cc8e22:

    # mc "Yeah, I guess there was some miscommunication. {w}I do know a few people who go to the University, though."
    mc "Yeah, saya rasa ada salah faham. {w}Saya tahu beberapa orang yang masuk ke Universiti."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:91
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_dd51247f:

    # mct "I wonder if Dahlia or Daisy would be interested in this place."
    mct "Saya tertanya-tanya adakah Dahlia atau Daisy akan berminat dengan tempat ini."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:93
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_5ce922b5:

    # mh "And if I had a place over by the College, what price range would you be looking at?"
    mh "Dan sekiranya saya mendapat tempat di Kolej, julat harga apa yang akan awak lihat?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:95
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_f0d17d70:

    # mc "Well, it's not for me. It's for my sister."
    mc "Ia bukan untuk saya. Ini untuk adik saya."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:97
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_60fe57ac:

    # mc "Well, it's not for me. It's for my friend."
    mc "Ia bukan untuk saya. Ini untuk rakan saya."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:99
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_9d92d73d:

    # mh "Your friend? Seriously?"
    mh "Kawan awak? Serius?"

