translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_5a37f8e5:

    # mc "Well, she's my oldest friend. We've known each other forever. She's almost like a little sister, but our parents never..."
    mc "Baiklah, dia adalah kawan tertua saya. Kami saling mengenali sudah lama. Dia hampir seperti adik perempuan saya, tapi ibu bapa kami tidak pernah..."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:102
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_c42fc760:

    # mh "Okay, so what are we doing here?"
    mh "Okay, jadi apa yang kita buat di sini?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:103
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_17eb9c77:

    # mc "I don't know. She's looking for a nice affordable place near the college, and she expects me to arrange it for her."
    mc "Saya tidak tahu. Dia mencari tempat berpatutan yang bagus berhampiran kolej, dan dia mengharapkan saya menguruskannya untuknya."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:105
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_829bd270:

    # mh "Well, there's a place near the College that I've been thinking about buying and fixing up... if we strike a deal, when could she move in?"
    mh "Jadi, ada tempat berhampiran Kolej yang telah saya fikirkan untuk beli dan perbaiki... jika kita membuat perjanjian, bila dia boleh masuk?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:106
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_40661ae5:

    # mc "Stacy arrives tomorrow, so literally anytime."
    mc "Stacy tiba esok, jadi bila-bila masa sahaja."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:108
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_83ff1077:

    # mh "Hmm. The paperwork is all ready, but I wouldn't be able to take ownership until Monday. Then it would take me a couple days..."
    mh "Hmm. Kertas kerja semuanya sudah siap, tapi saya tidak akan dapat mengambil alih sehingga Isnin. Maka saya akan mengambil masa beberapa hari..."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:109
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_83671762:

    # mc "A couple of days? That can't be right. {w}You already bought the place, didn't you?"
    mc "Beberapa hari? Itu tidak betul. {w}Awak sudah membeli tempat itu, bukan?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:111
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_79812529:

    # mh "Fine. You caught me lying. I already own the place, but I'm still having some work done on it. I don't know when it will be ready, but soon."
    mh "Baik. Awak telah menangkap saya berbohong. Saya sudah memiliki tempat itu, tapi saya masih menyelesaikannya. Saya tidak tahu bila ia akan siap, tetapi tidak lama lagi."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:112
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_f5d69345:

    # mc "What kind of place are we talking about?"
    mc "Apa jenis tempat yang kita bincangkan?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:114
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_f23f702c:

    # mh "One bedroom, one bathroom. All new appliances and fixtures. I already had the plumbing modernized and the electricity rewired... fresh drywall..."
    mh "Satu bilik tidur, satu bilik mandi. Semua peralatan dan kelengkapan baru. Saya telah memasang paip elektrik dan elektrik... drywall baharu..."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:115
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_b1b11b02:

    # mc "You're kidding me. Sounds like you sank a fortune into this already."
    mc "Awak bergurau dengan saya. Sepertinya awak sudah menghabiskan banyak duit untuk ini."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:117
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_b3c2ffe7:

    # mh "Does it? I wouldn't want to rent a place that I wouldn't live in..."
    mh "Adakah ia? Saya tidak mahu menyewa tempat yang tidak akan saya tinggali..."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:118
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_56399bc8:

    # mc "So, how much are you thinking rent would be?"
    mc "Jadi, berapakah jumlah wang sewa yang awak fikirkan?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:120
translate malaysian d05s05_apt2_ed0a972e:

    # mh "I triple checked all the math this time. The rent will be $1200/mo, which includes utilities."
    mh "Saya telah tiga kali memeriksa semua matematik kali ini. Sewa akan menjadi $1200/bulan, sekali dengan utiliti."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:137
translate malaysian d05s05_sympathy_41fbeee9:

    # mc "That sounds like a lot. Stacy is just a poor college student, couldn't you cut her a break?"
    mc "Ia kedengaran banyak. Stacy hanyalah pelajar kolej yang miskin, tidak bolehkah awak membantunya sedikit?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:139
translate malaysian d05s05_sympathy_55a1a228:

    # mh "I sympathize, but that's bad for business. If she can't afford the rent maybe she should try something else."
    mh "Saya bersimpati, tapi itu buruk untuk perniagaan. Sekiranya dia tidak dapat membayar sewa mungkin dia harus mencuba yang lain."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:140
translate malaysian d05s05_sympathy_38d17585:

    # mc "I'm sure she could afford the rent, if it was a little less... maybe $800/mo?"
    mc "Saya pasti dia mampu membayar sewa, jika ia sedikit lebih sedikit... mungkin $800/bulan?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:142
translate malaysian d05s05_sympathy_26f2d147:

    # mh "You want a lower price, that makes sense, but what you've just told me is that I might get stiffed and have to evict her. Too risky."
    mh "Awak mahukan harga yang lebih rendah, itu masuk akal, tapi apa yang baru saja anda katakan kepada saya ialah saya mungkin akan terkaku dan harus mengusirnya. Terlalu berisiko."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:143
translate malaysian d05s05_sympathy_ed28e768:

    # mct "Crap, that really backfired."
    mct "Aduh, masalah besar kalau begitu."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:150
translate malaysian d05s05_screwyourself_d310227f:

    # mc "It's a bit much, but $1200 might be manageable."
    mc "Ianya terlampau bankay, tapi $1200 mungkin dapat dikendalikan."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:152
translate malaysian d05s05_screwyourself_abbe76bc:

    # mh "Wait, she's starting college in the autumn? She'll be a freshman?"
    mh "Tunggu, dia memulakan kuliah pada musim luruh? Dia akan menjadi pelajar baru?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:153
translate malaysian d05s05_screwyourself_cf1adef2:

    # mc "Yeah."
    mc "Yeah."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:155
