    # mh "So, how about this: You co-sign the documents. She lives in the apartment for the Summer, and you move in at the beginning of the semester."
    mh "Jadi, bagaimana dengan ini: Awak menandatangani dokumen bersama. Dia tinggal di apartmen untuk musim panas, dan awak akan pindah pada awal semester."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:162
translate malaysian d05s05_screwyourself_f2e8b328:

    # mc "I... I suppose that could work."
    mc "Saya ... saya rasa ia boleh begitu."

