    # mc "You need to think about the future."
    mc "Anda perlu memikirkan tentang masa depan."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:180
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_6274e4f9:

    # mc "You've got yourself stuck with one beautiful apartment here that no one is renting, and you're already trying to do the same with the next place."
    mc "Awak telah terjebak dengan satu pangsapuri yang indah di sini yang tidak ada yang menyewa, dan awak sudah cuba melakukan perkara yang sama dengan tempat seterusnya."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:182
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_3b167374:

    # mh "Go on."
    mh "Teruskan."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:183
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_2945c8bd:

    # mc "You need advertising, sure, but more than that you need to build up a reputation."
    mc "Awak pasti memerlukan iklan, tapi lebih daripada itu awak perlu membina reputasi."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:184
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_eacba234:

    # mc "You need people to know that you can be relied upon. You need people to talk you up and think of you when they're looking to rent a place."
    mc "Awak memerlukan orang untuk mengetahui bahawa awak boleh dipercayai. Awak memerlukan orang untuk bercakap dengan awak dan memikirkan awak ketika mereka ingin menyewa tempat."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:186
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_61732d55:

    # mh "You're speaking in generalities. Get to the point."
    mh "Awak bercakap secara umum. Cakaplah sepenuhnya."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:187
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_b8c03784:

    # mc "Stacy isn't particularly popular in high school, but she's one of those wonderful, reliable, smart people that everyone will want to know in college."
    mc "Stacy tidak begitu popular di sekolah menengah, tetapi dia adalah antara orang yang hebat, boleh dipercayai, pintar yang ingin diketahui oleh semua orang di kolej."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:188
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_cd2d4b85:

    # mc "If she gets this apartment, then every freshmen is going to hear about it, and when they're looking for a place sophomore year they'll be knocking on your door."
    mc "Sekiranya dia mendapat pangsapuri ini, maka setiap pelajar baru akan mendengarnya, dan ketika mereka mencari tempat di tahun kedua, mereka akan mengetuk pintu awak."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:190
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_0ba6d803:

    # mh "Uh huh. And what is this goodwill and advertising going to cost me?"
    mh "Uh huh. Dan apakah niat baik dan pengiklanan ini akan membebankan saya??"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:191
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_7ec233dc:

    # mc "Not much. Just drop the rent down to $800/mo to ensure she has nothing but positive things to say about the place."
    mc "Tidak banyak. Turunkan harga sewa sehingga $800/bulan untuk memastikan dia tidak mempunyai apa-apa kecuali perkara positif yang boleh dinyatakan mengenai tempat itu."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:194
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_268106c2:

    # mh "You're a very persuasive young man."
    mh "Awak seorang pemuda yang sangat pandai memujuk."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:195
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_a7888ad7:

    # mc "Does that mean we have a deal?"
    mc "Adakah itu bermakna kita mempunyai perjanjian?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:197
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_512b5213:

    # mh "Sure, why not. I assume you'll want to see the place before she signs anything."
    mh "Baiklah, mengapa tidak. Saya menganggap awak pasti ingin melihat tempat itu sebelum dia menandatangani apa-apa."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:198
translate malaysian d05s05_capitalist_2bd6b602:

    # mc "Of course. Just call me when it's ready."
    mc "Semestinya. Hubungi saya apabila sudah siap."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:205
translate malaysian d05s05_end_2037a8c9:

    # mh "Vanessa's been on the phone for a while... {w}I hope everything is okay."
    mh "Vanessa telah lama  bercakap didalam telefon... {w}Saya harap semuanya baik-baik saja."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:206
translate malaysian d05s05_end_c6cf6bc0:

    # mc "It's probably about the first apartment she showed me today. There was a squatter who kinda trashed the place."
    mc "Ini mungkin mengenai apartmen pertama yang dia tunjukkan pada saya hari ini. Terdapat seorang setinggan yang agak menyepahkan tempat itu."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:209
translate malaysian d05s05_end_e462b279:

    # mh "That's awful! {w}She's probably going to be on the phone a long time dealing with that."
    mh "Sungguh mengerikan! {w} Dia mungkin sudah lama menelefonnya."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:210
translate malaysian d05s05_end_fc154ab8:

    # mc "Yeah. Can you tell her that we worked out a deal? I'm going to take off."
    mc "Yeah. Bolehkah awak memberitahunya bahawa kami telah membuat perjanjian? Saya akan pergi dahulu."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:212
translate malaysian d05s05_end_e46abdb8:

    # mh "Sure, sure. No problem."
    mh "Baiklah. Tiada masalah."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:214
translate malaysian d05s05_end_553f409b:

    # mh "Oh, [mcname], how did things work out for you at the Party the other night?"
    mh "Oh, [mcname], bagaimana keadaan awak di Parti malam itu?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:215
translate malaysian d05s05_end_5d1ba2f3:

    # mc "Terrific. Met the girl of my dreams, we stayed up talking all night, and have our first date tomorrow."
    mc "Hebat. Bertemu dengan gadis impian saya, kami terus berbual sepanjang malam, dan mempunyai temujanji pertama kami esok."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:217
translate malaysian d05s05_end_77f56a6c:

    # mh "Good for you! I hope you're taking her somewhere nice."
    mh "Baguslah untuk awak! Saya harap anda membawanya ke tempat yang bagus."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:218
translate malaysian d05s05_end_0b286d62:

    # mc "Do you know Nora's Coffee Shop?"
    mc "Awak tahu Kedai Kopi Nora?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:220
translate malaysian d05s05_end_0e90a45f:

    # mh "Seriously? You know that coffee dates aren't real dates."
    mh "Adakah awak bergurau? Awak tahu bahawa kurma kopi bukanlah temujanji yang sebenar."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:221
translate malaysian d05s05_end_6d93348e:

    # mc "Lydia will be performing there. I hooked her up with a gig, and we're going to have the date around her concert."
    mc "Lydia akan membuat persembahan di sana. Saya mengaitkannya dengan satu pertunjukan, dan kita akan bertemujanji selepas atau sebelum konsertnya."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:223
translate malaysian d05s05_end_68f427db:

    # mh "I stand corrected, that does sound... {w}Lydia? You don't mean Lydia Cox, do you?"
    mh "Betulkah apa yang saya dengar, ianya... {w}Lydia? Awak tidak bermaksud Lydia Cox, adakah awak?"

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:224
translate malaysian d05s05_end_95b68525:

    # mc "Yeah. She'll be singing at Nora's tomorrow evening."
    mc "Yeah. Dia akan menyanyi di kedai Nora pada malam esok."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:226
translate malaysian d05s05_end_8f7c2b52:

    # mh "Wow. Would you mind if I show up? Do I need to buy a ticket or..."
    mh "Wow. Adakah awak keberatan jika saya datang? Adakah saya perlu membeli tiket atau..."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:227
translate malaysian d05s05_end_25daa428:

    # mc "No ticket necessary. Just grab a drink while you're there."
    mc "Tidak perlu tiket. Hanya ambil minuman semasa awak berada di sana."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:229
translate malaysian d05s05_end_c5b86ed4:

    # mh "Cool. Maybe I'll mention it to a few people."
    mh "Terbaik. Mungkin saya akan sampaikannya kepada beberapa orang."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:231
translate malaysian d05s05_end_231838a7:

    # mc "Please do. Invite Vanessa when she gets off her call."
    mc "Silakan. Ajak Vanessa ketika dia habiskan panggilannya."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:232
translate malaysian d05s05_end_18d36efe:

    # mh "Thanks. Alright, well, I'll see you there."
    mh "Terima kasih. Baiklah, saya akan jumpa awak di sana."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:234
translate malaysian d05s05_end_020285ce:

    # mc "See ya', Lyssa."
    mc "Jumpa nanti, Lyssa."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:240
translate malaysian d05s05_end_5104b7e2:

    # mct "Alright, Stacy's got an apartment... or will have one soon."
    mct "Baiklah, Stacy ada sebuah pangsapuri ... atau akan segera memiliki satu."

# game/code/d05/d05s05b.rpy:241
translate malaysian d05s05_end_0fc82289:

    # mct "I can check that item off my worry list."
    mct "Saya dapat menyemak item itu dari senarai risau."

